On the podcast we talk with Darrell and Jake about optimizing your app’s paywall, how to increase revenue by giving users a better experience, tips for pricing your app, and how to reduce subscriber churn. We’re with Darrell Stone and Jake Mor in front of a live audience at the App Promotion Summit in New York City. The App Promotion Summit is America’s leading app marketing conference. Darrell is the Head of Product &amp; Design at Citizen, the number one public safety app in the U.S. Jake is the Founder &amp; CEO of Superwall, the best way to build in test paywalls without having to update your app.
